'''天主教貝洛奧里藏特總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Bellohorizontina}}；{{lang-pt|Arquidiocese de Belo Horizonte}}）是[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]在[[巴西|巴西]]的一個教省[[總教區|總教區]]，下轄四個教區。

總教區位於[[米納斯吉拉斯州|米納斯吉拉斯州]]中部，教座位於首府[[貝洛奧里藏特|貝洛奧里藏特]]。2006年有教友3,535,715人，佔轄區總人口75.0%。教區下轄258個堂區，有609名司鐸。現任總主教為{{link-en|瓦爾莫·奧利韋拉-德-阿澤維多|Walmor Oliveira de Azevedo}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 28.01.2004 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/01/28/0044/00147.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-10-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191030190352/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/01/28/0044/00147.html |archivedate=2019-10-30 |language=it |date=2004-01-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-pt|若亞敬·若望·莫爾-吉馬朗埃斯|Joaquim Giovanni Mol Guimarães}}、{{link-de|熱奧瓦內·類斯·達-西爾瓦|Geovane Luís da Silva}}和{{link-de|雲先·費雷拉|Vicente de Paula Ferreira}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 11.02.2006 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2006/02/11/0073/00211.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-10-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191030185651/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2006/02/11/0073/00211.html |archivedate=2019-10-30 |language=it |date=2006-02-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Other Pontifical Acts, 21.12.2016 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2016/12/21/161221d.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-10-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191030182512/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2016/12/21/161221d.html |archivedate=2019-10-30 |language=en |date=2016-12-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 08.03.2017 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2017/03/08/170308a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-10-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191030180920/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2017/03/08/170308a.html |archivedate=2019-10-30 |language=en |date=2017-03-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休輔理主教為{{link-pt|施巴士坦·羅格·拉貝洛-門德斯|Sebastião Roque Rabelo Mendes}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 15.12.2004 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/12/15/0605/01979.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-10-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191030190649/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/12/15/0605/01979.html |archivedate=2019-10-30 |language=it |date=2004-12-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

教區於1921年2月11日成立<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |volume=XIII |year=1921 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=336-338 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-13-1921-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-06-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611115417/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-13-1921-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-06-11 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1924年2月1日升為總教區<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |volume=XVI |year=1924 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=264-265 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-16-1924-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-06-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611122923/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-16-1924-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-06-11 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

